metadata.name: New Year's Card 2023
metadata.description:
On the night of December 31, tired from his busy work schedule, he drank sake and fell asleep.  
When he woke up on New Year's morning, he found the rabbit god, this year's zodiac sign, biting his paycheck.  
ｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰ

This is the NFT art for the year 2023. 
My best wishes to you all for a good New Year's Day!
